NBeersManager

Packages 
Package Description
org.nbena.beersmanager.conf
This package contains the two classes necessary to work with configuration.
org.nbena.beersmanager.coreclasses
This package contains the 4 classes that are necessary to represent beers, breweries and beer style.
org.nbena.beersmanager.exceptions
This package contains the custom exception that can be thrown by the program.
org.nbena.beersmanager.exe
This package contains the two classes necessary to the "runtime".
org.nbena.beersmanager.exe.ui
This package basically contains just a class, the controller in the MVC paradigm.
org.nbena.beersmanager.exe.ui.models
Here there are all the "model" classes of the MVC paradigm.
org.nbena.beersmanager.exe.ui.views
Here there all the GUI classes.
org.nbena.beersmanager.export
This package contains all the classes necessary to export data in various formats.
org.nbena.beersmanager.json.conf
This package contains the classes that takes care of saving and reading the program's configuration
into and from a JSON file.
org.nbena.beersmanager.json.coreclasses
This package contains the classes that takes care of saving/reading data into/from JSON files, one for beers, one for breweries and one for styles.
org.nbena.beersmanager.query
This package contains the two classes necessary to: Filter data Sort data Search data
org.nbena.beersmanager.sclasses
This package contains classes that are a modified version of their original class
due to the fact the some operations need a modified version.
